對 質 時 ， 直 指 對 方 最 拿 手 是 「 炒 反 手 排 骨 」 。"},{"pid":"0458f4b9e5e3896992549305a0352857e66028ea","tid":267461,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"唔大勢力既都唔會出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4c5bfacfa84f800a3d8fa126f9ed9abe1e49b7","tid":267461,"uid":118714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dc901434aba30063a46a13a7f447145baa69d95","tid":267461,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淨係睇肥姐同koei既關係你就知佢唔野小啦</blockquote><br />\nkoei<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暗榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}